 request,but nothing goes well with that old session.Probably you are missing one point.Everytime you are saying that I just can logout the remote user.But this is not.When 5-6 thread per second will run with the old session,it will be impossible for that remote user to login into his account.\nWhat solution do you have for that user,who can not login into his account with valid password?","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2015-02-25T12:32:43.235Z","updated_at":"2015-02-25T12:32:43.235Z","actor":{"username":"siddiki","cleared":true,"url":"/siddiki","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/502/cf522f55c77430ca80c9ff947d022eb7e3d79350_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":342594,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Any thought on this ticket?","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2015-02-27T23:55:21.415Z","updated_at":"2015-02-27T23:55:21.415Z","actor":{"username":"siddiki","cleared":true,"url":"/siddiki","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/502/cf522f55c77430ca80c9ff947d022eb7e3d79350_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":344046,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"@siddiki we're still working on this. It might take a while, sorry.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2015-03-02T08:49:38.076Z","updated_at":"2015-03-02T08:49:38.076Z","actor":{"username":"jens","cleared":false,"url":"/jens","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"h